Knowledge Base Mühendislikleri İçin Özelleştirilmiş Yetenek Değerlendirme Sistemi
1. Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (BM) - Özel Assessment Kriterleri
Temel Yetenek Testleri:

Programming Fundamentals (40% ağırlık)

C/C++ programming logic
Data structures implementation
Algorithm analysis ve complexity
Object-oriented programming concepts


Mathematical & Logical Reasoning (25% ağırlık)

Discrete mathematics
Boolean algebra
Binary arithmetic
Pattern recognition


System Thinking (20% ağırlık)

Computer organization concepts
Digital logic understanding
Problem decomposition ability


Technical Aptitude (15% ağırlık)

Debugging capability
Code optimization mindset
Software engineering principles



Mülakat Özel Soruları:

"Debug this code segment"
"Design a simple algorithm"
"Explain computer architecture"


2. Elektronik ve Haberleşme Mühendisliği (EHM) - Özel Assessment Kriterleri
Temel Yetenek Testleri:

Circuit Analysis (35% ağırlık)

Analog circuit understanding
Digital electronics basics
Signal processing concepts
Electromagnetic theory


Mathematical Foundation (25% ağırlık)

Complex numbers
Fourier transforms
Differential equations
Linear algebra


Technical Problem Solving (25% ağırlık)

Circuit design logic
Signal analysis
Frequency domain thinking


Communication Systems (15% ağırlık)

Modulation concepts
Network protocols
RF principles



Praktik Testler:

"Analyze this circuit"
"Design a simple amplifier"
"Explain signal modulation"


3. Siber Güvenlik Mühendisliği (SGM) - Özel Assessment Kriterleri
Temel Yetenek Testleri:

Security Thinking (30% ağırlık)

Threat analysis mindset
Risk assessment capability
Attack vector understanding
Defensive strategy planning


Technical Skills (30% ağırlık)

Network security protocols
Cryptography basics
System vulnerabilities
Ethical hacking concepts


Programming & Scripting (25% ağırlık)

Python for security
Bash scripting
Network programming
Automation skills


Analytical Reasoning (15% ağırlık)

Pattern detection
Logical reasoning
Incident response



Senario-Based Tests:

"How would you secure this network?"
"Identify vulnerabilities in this code"
"Design a security protocol"


4. Yapay Zeka ve Veri Mühendisliği (YZVM) - Özel Assessment Kriterleri
Temel Yetenek Testleri:

Mathematical Foundation (35% ağırlık)

Statistics & probability
Linear algebra
Calculus
Optimization theory


Programming & Data Skills (30% ağırlık)

Python mastery
Data manipulation (Pandas, NumPy)
SQL database skills
Algorithm implementation


Machine Learning Concepts (25% ağırlık)

Supervised/unsupervised learning
Model evaluation
Feature engineering
Deep learning basics


Problem-Solving Approach (10% ağırlık)

Data-driven thinking
Experimental design
Result interpretation



Hands-on Assessments:

"Analyze this dataset"
"Implement a simple ML model"
"Design a data pipeline"


5. Kontrol ve Otomasyon Mühendisliği (KOM) - Özel Assessment Kriterleri
Temel Yetenek Testleri:

Control Systems Theory (30% ağırlık)

Feedback control concepts
System stability analysis
Transfer functions
State space methods


Programming & Automation (25% ağırlık)

PLC programming (Ladder Logic)
SCADA systems
HMI design
Industrial protocols


Electrical & Mechanical Systems (25% ağırlık)

Motor control
Sensor technology
Actuator systems
Power electronics


Industrial Application (20% ağırlık)

Process control
Robotics basics
Safety systems
Manufacturing concepts



Practical Evaluations:

"Program this PLC logic"
"Design a control system"
"Troubleshoot this automation"


6. Robotik ve Otonom Sistemleri Mühendisliği (ROSM) - Özel Assessment Kriterleri
Temel Yetenek Testleri:

Robotics Fundamentals (30% ağırlık)

Kinematics & dynamics
Path planning
Robot programming
Sensor integration


Programming & AI (25% ağırlık)

Python/C++ for robotics
ROS (Robot Operating System)
Machine learning for robots
Computer vision


Mathematical Modeling (25% ağırlık)

Linear algebra
Probability theory
Control theory
Signal processing


System Integration (20% ağırlık)

Hardware-software interface
Multi-sensor fusion
Real-time systems
Safety protocols




🎯 Entegre Değerlendirme Metodolojisi
Aşama 1: Online Pre-Assessment (60 dakika)

Bölüm-spesifik aptitude testi
Temel matematik yetkinliği
Programlama logic testi
Problem çözme senaryoları

Aşama 2: Hands-on Technical Test (90 dakika)

Bölüme özgü praktik problemler
Kod yazma/devre analizi/veri analizi
Real-world scenario çözümü

Aşama 3: Yapılandırılmış Mülakat (75 dakika)

Technical deep-dive sorular
Project-based discussions
Problem-solving approach
Career motivation assessment

Aşama 4: Personality & Interest Profiling (45 dakika)

Holland Code (RIASEC) assessment
Big Five personality test
Work style preferences
Learning approach evaluation

🔍 Bölüm-Spesifik Başarı Kriterleri
Mühendislik DalıMinimum Başarı SkoruKritik Yetenek AlanlarıAğırlık DağılımıBilgisayar75/100Programming, Logic, Math40-25-20-15Elektronik70/100Circuits, Math, Signals35-25-25-15Siber Güvenlik80/100Security, Technical, Programming30-30-25-15AI & Veri85/100Math, Programming, ML35-30-25-10Kontrol70/100Control, Programming, Systems30-25-25-20Robotik75/100Robotics, Programming, Math30-25-25-20
Bu sistemle her mühendislik dalının kendine özgü yetenek ve ilgi alanlarını doğru bir şekilde değerlendirerek, öğrencilere en uygun bölümü önerebiliriz.
